EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello {!Opportunity.Contact__c},
Attached to this email is the Federal Tax form that you, or your accountant will need to complete in order to take advantage of the Federal solar tax credits.
You will need to include the cost of your solar system which is... {!Opportunity.Amount}
Please call the Palmetto Customer Care Department, or consult your CPA if you have any further questions about your tax forms.
Sincerely,
Palmetto Customer Care Team customer.care@palmetto.com Phone: 855-339-1831 Office: 843-720-1844
